are that boys can be sexually abused. One boy stated, \u201cI thought it could never happen to boys.\u201d As a result, the boys who are abused are deeply ashamed.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "2682d3c2-1016-490c-b123-5e6895e7add7": {"__data__": {"id_": "2682d3c2-1016-490c-b123-5e6895e7add7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/deoum-troung-pram-hath-modern-cambodia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Deoum Troung Pram Hath in Modern Cambodia", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/deoum-troung-pram-hath-modern-cambodia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "2c040df80dc012d45963291c716a3bdc726a71bee48cd465d2b48d5d8de36d4d"}, "2": {"node_id": "33746639-8678-4fda-8e14-d305a6f27d57", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/deoum-troung-pram-hath-modern-cambodia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b5637382fab602b4988c9baa9c3923256c02d5fe1ae515d02589d76e747f0ea4"}}, "hash": "0e3f9d88a7f55aa1c8d2375cad9a9485d0b877cff7bca4cd03564ba0e6b58f2d", "text": "In the words of one boy \u201cI blame myself ... I\u2019m a male.\u201d27 In contrast, these boys said that they were vulnerable and needed protection.28 \u201cBoys can\u2018t cry out. If we cry, they say we are weak, but they don\u2019t know how much hurt we have,\u201d one boy said.29 These attitudes make it difficult for boys to seek